mcp-proxy.js — child MCP process lifecycle manager

class MCPProxyManager
  constructor()→void|init servers map, monitors set, pending requests
  loadConfig()→void|read ~/.gemini/agent-portal.json, populate servers map
  startAllServers(callback)→void|spawn all configured child servers
  spawnServer(serverName)→void|fork child via spawn, wire stdio, track PID
  sendToChild(serverName,msg)→void|write JSON-RPC msg to child stdin
  requestFromChild(serverName,method,params)→Promise<obj>|send request, wait for response (5s timeout)
  getInstances()→arr|list all servers with name,prefix,command,args,pid
  broadcastMonitor(msg)→void|send event to all connected WS monitors
  handleUpgrade(req,socket,head)→bool|route WS upgrade to monitor handler
  handleMonitor(serverName,req,socket,head)→void|create WS monitor connection

PATTERNS: child process management|stdio JSON-RPC|WS monitoring|pending request map
DEPS: ws|node:child_process|local config file
